# Plan 19: Missing Features & Enhancements

## Goal

Implement additional features and pages that were identified as missing from the initial 18 plans.

## Tasks

- [x] Create Admin Dashboard (`app/admin/page.tsx`):

  - [x] Overview cards showing total releases, posts, events, subscribers.
  - [x] Recent activity feed.
  - [x] Quick stats visualization.
  - [x] Use **ShadCN Card** for stat blocks.

- [x] Create Contact Page (`app/contact/page.tsx`):

  - [x] Contact form with name, email, subject, message fields.
  - [x] Use **ShadCN Form** with Zod validation.
  - [x] Booking inquiry option.
  - [x] Server action to handle submissions.

- [x] Create Legal Pages:

  - [x] `app/privacy/page.tsx` (Privacy Policy).
  - [x] `app/terms/page.tsx` (Terms of Service).

- [ ] Add File Upload Functionality:

  - [ ] Create upload API route for images/audio.
  - [ ] Integrate with admin forms (replace URL inputs).
  - [ ] Store files in public directory or cloud storage.

- [x] Add Admin Settings Page (`app/admin/settings/page.tsx`):

  - [x] Manage social media links.
  - [x] Edit about page content.
  - [x] Update site metadata.
  - [x] Configure general settings.

- [x] Add Social Sharing:

  - [x] Share buttons on blog posts (Twitter, Facebook, LinkedIn).
  - [x] Share buttons on music releases.
  - [x] Copy link functionality.

- [x] Create Press Kit Page (`app/press/page.tsx`):

  - [x] Downloadable press kit (bio, photos, logos).
  - [x] High-res images for media.
  - [x] Press contact information.

- [ ] Add Global Search:

  - [ ] Search across music, blog posts, events.
  - [ ] Use **ShadCN Command** for search UI.
  - [ ] Implement fuzzy search.

- [ ] Analytics Integration:

  - [ ] Add Google Analytics or Plausible.
  - [ ] Track page views, music plays, etc.

- [ ] Performance Optimizations:
  - [ ] Image optimization and lazy loading.
  - [ ] Code splitting and bundle optimization.
  - [ ] Implement caching strategies.
